B%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/T%E1%BA%B7ng-th%E1%BA%BF-t%E1%BB%AD-Th%C3%A1i-h%C6%B0-t%E1%BB%AD/poem-YIeYyP6-54MlZXYwHfxVQw">Tặng thế tử Thái hư tử - 贈世子太虛子</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/V%C4%83n-T%E1%BB%AD-Ph%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/author--NGvGpUybUt1BWdtQz2IMg">Văn Tử Phương</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/T%E1%BA%B7ng-Tr%E1%BB%8Bnh-th%E1%BA%ADp-b%C3%A1t-Ph%E1%BA%A7n/poem-iNvJ6tBHRWQrfqVP1mxB_Q">Tặng Trịnh thập bát Phần - 贈鄭十八賁</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Thu-d%C3%A3-k%E1%BB%B3-1/poem-rPRFSrqaI6wGmBHVDVXebg">Thu dã kỳ 1 - 秋野其一</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
